'''2014年[[保加利亚|保加利亚]]议会选举'''在10月5日举行，选举产生第43届[[国民议会_(保加利亚)|国民议会]]。<ref name="Sofia News Agency">{{cite web|title=Bulgaria's 42nd Parliament Dissolved, Elections on October 5|url=http://www.novinite.com/articles/162542/Bulgaria%27s+42nd+Parliament+Dissolved%2C+Elections+on+October+5|website=Novinite.com|publisher=Sofia News Agency|accessdate=9 August 2014|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907083843/https://www.novinite.com/articles/162542/Bulgaria%27s+42nd+Parliament+Dissolved%2C+Elections+on+October+5|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[保加利亚欧洲发展公民党|争取欧洲进步公民党]]（GERB）保持第一大党地位，获得大约三分之一的选票，赢得240个席位中的84席。此次选举一共有八个党派赢得席位，为1990年首次民主选举以来政党最多的一届议会。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Petrov|first1=Angel|title=Bulgaria's Grand Parliament Chessboard Might Be Both Ailment and Cure|url=http://www.novinite.com/articles/163898/Bulgaria%27s+Grand+Parliament+Chessboard+Might+Be+Both+Ailment+and+Cure|website=Novinite.com|publisher=Sofia News Agency|accessdate=7 October 2014|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907081534/https://www.novinite.com/articles/163898/Bulgaria%27s+Grand+Parliament+Chessboard+Might+Be+Both+Ailment+and+Cure|dead-url=no}}</ref>GERB的[[博伊科·鲍里索夫|博伊科·鲍里索夫]]与[[改革者集团|改革者集团]]（Reformist Bloc）联盟，并得到组成爱国阵线和保加利亚复兴第二条道路的支持，组成新一届政府。

==背景==

[[2013年保加利亚议会选举|2013年选举]]后，[[普拉门·奥雷沙尔斯基|普拉门·奥雷沙尔斯基]]组成由[[保加利亚社会党|保加利亚社会党]]（BSP）和[[权利与自由运动|权利与自由运动]]（DPS）的联合政府，但只获得一半的议会席位支持。为应对选举，116名议员推选DPS议员、媒体大亨[[德梁·佩耶夫斯基|德梁·佩耶夫斯基]]）（Delyan Peevski）为国家安全局长。<ref name="reuters">[http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/06/14/us-bulgaria-government-idUSBRE95D0ML20130614 Bulgarians protests over media magnate as security chief] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/06/14/us-bulgaria-government-idUSBRE95D0ML20130614 |date=20151001133430 }}, Reuters, 14 June 2013</ref><ref>[http://www.novinite.com/view_news.php?id=151268 Thousands Rally in Bulgaria against Election of Shady Mogul for 'FBI' Head] {{Wayback|url=http://www.novinite.com/view_news.php?id=151268 |date=20170202084910 }}, Novinite, 14 June 2013</ref><ref name="bgnes1">{{bg icon}} [http://video.bgnes.com/view/41781 Protester says things could change for better (video)] {{Wayback|url=http://video.bgnes.com/view/41781 |date=20141006081939 }}, bgnes, 14 June 2013</ref>此举被视为私人利益控制公共机构的证据。尽管随后政府撤回了任命，但已经太迟，大量抗议者涌上街头，要求内阁辞职<ref>{{cite web|title=保加利亚百名议员和部长遭抗议者围困长达8小时|url=http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2013/07/25/5411s4194941.htm|website=Novinite.com|publisher=国际在线|accessdate=2013-07-25|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912020959/http://news.cri.cn/gb/42071/2013/07/25/5411s4194941.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，奥雷沙尔斯基政府于2013年6月14日开始面临一系列的抗议活动。

保加利亚社会党在欧洲议会选举中遭受挫折后（只获得18.94%的选票，低于2013年的26.6%），反对党呼吁提前举行议会选举<ref>{{cite web|title=Bulgarian Co-ruling Party DPS Calls for Early Elections by end-2014|url=http://www.novinite.com/articles/161086/Bulgarian+Co-ruling+Party+DPS+Calls+for+Early+Elections+by+end-2014|website=Novinite.com|publisher=Sofia News Agency|accessdate=5 June 2014|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907025612/https://www.novinite.com/articles/161086/Bulgarian+Co-ruling+Party+DPS+Calls+for+Early+Elections+by+end-2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年6月10日，保加利亚社会党领袖[[谢尔盖·斯塔尼舍夫|谢尔盖·斯塔尼舍夫]]也要求政府辞职<ref name=Resign>{{cite web|title=BSP Leader Stanishev Demands Government Resignation, July Elections|url=http://www.novinite.com/articles/161192/BSP+Leader+Stanishev+Demands+Government+Resignation%2C+July+Elections|website=Novinite.com|publisher=Sofia News Agency|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907074939/https://www.novinite.com/articles/161192/BSP+Leader+Stanishev+Demands+Government+Resignation%2C+July+Elections|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

6月17日召开的国家安全咨询委员会特别会议上，[[保加利亚总统|保加利亚总统]]、总理与议会各大政党达成共识，认为保加利亚需要一个平稳过渡期实现政治稳定，决定提前举行议会选举<ref>{{cite web|title=President Plevneliev Urges Outgoing Parliament to Review Budget|url=http://www.novinite.com/articles/161878/President+Plevneliev+Urges+Outgoing+Parliament+to+Review+Budget|website=Novinite.com|publisher=Sofia News Agency|accessdate=9 July 2014|archive-date=2020-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107224206/https://www.novinite.com/articles/161878/President+Plevneliev+Urges+Outgoing+Parliament+to+Review+Budget|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并确定8月6日解散议会、组建看守政府。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bulgarian Gov't to Resign between July 23, 25 - PM Oresharski|url=http://www.novinite.com/articles/161825/Bulgarian+Gov%27t+to+Resign+between+July+23%2C+25+-+PM+Oresharski|website=Novinite.com|publisher=Sofia News Agency|accessdate=9 July 2014|archive-date=2020-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107170157/https://www.novinite.com/articles/161825/Bulgarian+Gov't+to+Resign+between+July+23,+25+-+PM+Oresharski|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月23日星期三，奥雷沙尔斯基政府递交了辞呈<ref>{{cite web|title=Bulgaria's PM Plamen Oresharski Resigns|url=http://www.novinite.com/articles/162217/Bulgaria%27s+PM+Plamen+Oresharski+Resigns|website=Novinite.com|publisher=Sofia News Agency|accessdate=25 July 2014|archive-date=2020-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107143429/https://www.novinite.com/articles/162217/Bulgaria's+PM+Plamen+Oresharski+Resigns|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第二天议会以180票对8票（8人投了弃权票和44人缺席）接受政府辞职<ref>{{cite web|title=Bulgarian Parliament Approves Government Resignation|url=http://www.novinite.com/articles/162218/Bulgarian+Parliament+Approves+Government+%3Cb%3EResignation%3C/b%3E|website=Novinite.com|publisher=Sofia News Agency|accessdate=25 July 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192809/http://www.novinite.com/articles/162218/Bulgarian+Parliament+Approves+Government+%3Cb%3EResignation%3C/b%3E|dead-url=no}}</ref>。经过多次组阁难产，8月6日[[格奥尔基·布里兹纳什基|格奥尔基·布里兹纳什基]]领导的过渡政府宣誓就职，第42国民议会解散，选举日期定于10月5日。<ref name="Sofia News Agency"/>

