==政府组成==
新当选的议会议员于10月27日首次举行会议。<ref>[http://www.standartnews.com/english/read/bulgarias_43th_national_assembly_to_be_inaugurated_today_-5999.html Bulgaria's {{sic|43|th|nolink=yes}} National Assembly to be inaugurated todayКопирано от standartnews.com] {{Wayback|url=http://www.standartnews.com/english/read/bulgarias_43th_national_assembly_to_be_inaugurated_today_-5999.html |date=20150924120307 }} Standart, 27 October 2014</ref>

鲍里索夫的GERB与改革者集团联盟，外部支持的有爱国阵线和保加利亚复兴第二条道路，在向总统[[罗森·普列夫内利耶夫|罗森·普列夫内利耶夫]]提交内阁名单后，正式组建新政府。20名内阁部长以136票 - 97票（一票弃权）获得通过<ref>{{cite web|title=Bulgarian MPs Approve New Cabinet, Ministers Sworn In|url=http://www.novinite.com/articles/164611/Bulgarian+MPs+Approve+New+Cabinet%2C+Ministers+Sworn+In|website=Novinite.com|publisher=Sofia News Agency|accessdate=7 November 2014|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925004739/https://www.novinite.com/articles/164611/Bulgarian+MPs+Approve+New+Cabinet,+Ministers+Sworn+In|dead-url=no}}</ref>，鲍里索夫总理提名通过投票为149票 - 85票。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bulgaria's Parliament Approves New Government|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/bulgarias-parliament-approves-government-26753557|website=abcnews.go.com|publisher=ABC News Internet Ventures|accessdate=7 November 2014|archive-date=2014-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112144734/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/bulgarias-parliament-approves-government-26753557|dead-url=no}}</ref>

